    },
    "innerText": "9. Opammasaṃyuttaṃ"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "1. Kūṭasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "223"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Kūṭaṃ"
      },
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "gacchantī"
      },
      "ti kūṭacchiddassa anupavisanavasena kūṭaṃ gacchanti. Yā ca gopānasiyo gopānasantaragatā, tāpi kūṭaṃ āhacca ṭhānena ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "kūṭaṅgamā"
      },
      ". Duvidhāpi kūṭe samosaraṇā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Kūṭassa samugghātena"
      },
      " vināsena bhijjanena. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Avijjāya samugghātenā"
      },
      "ti avijjāya accantameva appavattiyā. Tena ca mokkhadhammādhigamena tadanurūpadhammādhigamo dassito. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Appamattā"
      },
      "ti pana iminā tassa upāyo dassito."
    ],
    "innerText": "223.Kūṭaṃgacchantīti kūṭacchiddassa anupavisanavasena kūṭaṃ gacchanti. Yā ca gopānasiyo gopānasantaragatā, tāpi kūṭaṃ āhacca ṭhānena kūṭaṅgamā. Duvidhāpi kūṭe samosaraṇā. Kūṭassa samugghātena vināsena bhijjanena. Avijjāya samugghātenāti avijjāya accantameva appavattiyā. Tena ca mokkhadhammādhigamena tadanurūpadhammādhigamo dassito. Appamattāti pana iminā tassa upāyo dassito."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Kūṭasuttavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "2. Nakhasikhasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "224"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Evaṃ appakā"
      },
      " yathā nakhasikhāya āropitapaṃsu, sugatisaṃvattaniyassa kammassa appakattā ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "evaṃ devesupī"
      },
      "ti hīnūdāharaṇavasena vuttaṃ. Appatarā hi sattā ye devesu jāyanti, tañca kho kāmadevesu. Itaresu pana vattabbameva natthi."
    ],
    "innerText": "224.Evaṃ appakā yathā nakhasikhāya āropitapaṃsu, sugatisaṃvattaniyassa kammassa appakattā evaṃ devesupīti hīnūdāharaṇavasena vuttaṃ. Appatarā hi sattā ye devesu jāyanti, tañca kho kāmadevesu. Itaresu pana vattabbameva natthi."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Nakhasikhasuttavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "3. Kulasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "225"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Vidhaṃsayanti"
      },
      " viheṭhayanti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Vaḍḍhitā"
      },
      "ti bhāvanāpāripūrivasena paribrūhitā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Punappunaṃ katā"
      },
      "ti bhāvanāya bahulīkaraṇena aparāparaṃ pavattitā ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "yuttayānaṃ viya katā"
      },
      "ti yathā yuttaṃ ājaññarathaṃ chekena sārathinā adhiṭṭhitaṃ yathāruci pavattati, evaṃ yathāruci pavattiyā gamitā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Patiṭṭhānaṭṭhenā"
      },
      "ti adhiṭṭhānaṭṭhena. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Vatthu viya katā"
      },
      " sabbaso upakkilesavisodhanena suvisodhitamariyādaṃ viya katā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Adhiṭṭhitā"
      },
      "ti paṭipakkhadūrībhāvato subhāvitabhāvena avikampaneyyatāya ṭhapitā ",
      ". ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Samantato citā"
      },
      "ti sabbabhāgena bhāvanūpacayaṃ gamitā. Tenāha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘suvaḍḍhitā’’"
      },
      "ti ",
      ". ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Suṭṭhu samāraddhā"
      },
      "ti mettābhāvanāya matthakappattiyā sammadeva sampāditā."
    ],
    "innerText": "225.Vidhaṃsayanti viheṭhayanti. Vaḍḍhitāti bhāvanāpāripūrivasena paribrūhitā. Punappunaṃ katāti bhāvanāya bahulīkaraṇena aparāparaṃ pavattitā yuttayānaṃ viya katāti yathā yuttaṃ ājaññarathaṃ chekena sārathinā adhiṭṭhitaṃ yathāruci pavattati, evaṃ yathāruci pavattiyā gamitā. Patiṭṭhānaṭṭhenāti adhiṭṭhānaṭṭhena. Vatthu viya katā sabbaso upakkilesavisodhanena suvisodhitamariyādaṃ viya katā. Adhiṭṭhitāti paṭipakkhadūrībhāvato subhāvitabhāvena avikampaneyyatāya ṭhapitā . Samantato citāti sabbabhāgena bhāvanūpacayaṃ gamitā. Tenāha ‘‘suvaḍḍhitā’’ti . Suṭṭhu samāraddhāti mettābhāvanāya matthakappattiyā sammadeva sampāditā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Kulasuttavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "4. Okkhāsuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "226"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Mahāmukhaukkhalīna"
      },
      "nti mahāmukhānaṃ mahantakoḷumbānaṃ sataṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Paṇītabhojanabharitāna"
      },
      "nti sappimadhusakkarādīhi upanītapaṇītabhojanehi paripuṇṇānaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Tassā"
      },
      "ti pāṭhassa. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Goduhanamatta"
      },
      "nti godohanavelāmattaṃ. Taṃ pana kittakaṃ adhippetanti āha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘gāviyā’’"
      },
      "tiādi. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Sabbasattesu hitapharaṇa"
      },
      "nti anodhisomettābhāvanamāha – mettacittaṃ appanāppattaṃ bhāvetuṃ sakkotīti adhippāyo. Tampi tato yathāvuttadānato ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "mahapphalatara"
      },
      "nti."
    ],
    "innerText": "226.Mahāmukhaukkhalīnanti mahāmukhānaṃ mahantakoḷumbānaṃ sataṃ. Paṇītabhojanabharitānanti sappimadhusakkarādīhi upanītapaṇītabhojanehi paripuṇṇānaṃ. Tassāti pāṭhassa. Goduhanamattanti godohanavelāmattaṃ. Taṃ pana kittakaṃ adhippetanti āha ‘‘gāviyā’’tiādi. Sabbasattesu hitapharaṇanti anodhisomettābhāvanamāha – mettacittaṃ appanāppattaṃ bhāvetuṃ sakkotīti adhippāyo. Tampi tato yathāvuttadānato mahapphalataranti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Okkhāsuttavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "5. Sattisuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "227"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Agge paharitvā"
      },
      "ti tiṇhaphalasattiyā agge hatthena vā muṭṭhinā vā pahāraṃ datvā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Kappāsavaṭṭiṃ viyā"
      },
      "ti pahatakappāsapiṇḍaṃ viya. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Niyyāsavaṭṭiṃ viyā"
      },
      "ti phalasaṇṭhānaṃ niyyāsapiṇḍaṃ viya. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Ekato katvā"
      },
      "ti kalikādibhāvena vīsatiṃsapiṇḍāni ekajjhaṃ katvā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Alliyāpento"
      },
      " piṇḍaṃ karonto. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Paṭileṇetī"
      },
      "ti paṭilīnayati nāmeti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Alliyāpento"
      },
      " te dvepi dhārā ekato samphusāpento. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Paṭikoṭṭetī"
      },
      "ti paṭipaharati. Tattha khaṇḍaṃ viya niyyāso. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Kappāsavaṭṭanakaraṇīya"
      },
      "nti vihatassa kappāsassa paṭisaṃharaṇavasena bandhanadaṇḍaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Pavattento"
      },
      "ti kappāsassa saṃvellanavasena pavattento."
    ],
    "innerText": "227.Agge paharitvāti tiṇhaphalasattiyā agge hatthena vā muṭṭhinā vā pahāraṃ datvā. Kappāsavaṭṭiṃ viyāti pahatakappāsapiṇḍaṃ viya. Niyyāsavaṭṭiṃ viyāti phalasaṇṭhānaṃ niyyāsapiṇḍaṃ viya. Ekato katvāti kalikādibhāvena vīsatiṃsapiṇḍāni ekajjhaṃ katvā. Alliyāpento piṇḍaṃ karonto. Paṭileṇetīti paṭilīnayati nāmeti. Alliyāpento te dvepi dhārā ekato samphusāpento. Paṭikoṭṭetīti paṭipaharati. Tattha khaṇḍaṃ viya niyyāso. Kappāsavaṭṭanakaraṇīyanti vihatassa kappāsassa paṭisaṃharaṇavasena bandhanadaṇḍaṃ. Pavattentoti kappāsassa saṃvellanavasena pavattento."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Sattisuttavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "6. Dhanuggahasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "228"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Daḷhadhanuno"
      },
      "ti ",
      " thirataradhanuno. Idāni tassa thiratarabhāvaṃ paricchedato dassetuṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘daḷhadhanū’’"
      },
      "tiādi vuttaṃ. Tattha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "dvisahassathāma"
      },
      "nti palānaṃ dvisahassathāmaṃ. Vuttamevatthaṃ pākaṭataraṃ katvā dassetuṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘yassā’’"
      },
      "tiādimāha. Tattha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "yassā"
      },
      "ti dhanuno. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Āropitassā"
      },
      "ti jiyaṃ āropitassa. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Jiyābaddho"
      },
      "ti jiyāya baddho. Pathavito muccati, etaṃ ‘‘dvisahassathāma’’nti veditabbaṃ ",
      ". ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Lohasīsādīna"
      },
      "nti kāḷalohatambalohasīsādīnaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Bhāro"
      },
      "ti purisabhāro, so pana majjhimapurisassa vasena edisaṃ tassa balaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Uggahitasippā"
      },
      " dhanuvedasikkhāvasena. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Ciṇṇavasībhāvā"
      },
      " lakkhesu avirajjhanasarakkhepavasena. Kataṃ rājakulādīsu upagantvā asanaṃ sarakkhepo etehīti ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "katūpasanā"
      },
      "ti āha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘rājakulādīsu dassitasippā’’"
      },
      "ti."
    ],
    "innerText": "228.Daḷhadhanunoti thirataradhanuno. Idāni tassa thiratarabhāvaṃ paricchedato dassetuṃ ‘‘daḷhadhanū’’tiādi vuttaṃ. Tattha dvisahassathāmanti palānaṃ dvisahassathāmaṃ. Vuttamevatthaṃ pākaṭataraṃ katvā dassetuṃ ‘‘yassā’’tiādimāha. Tattha yassāti dhanuno. Āropitassāti jiyaṃ āropitassa. Jiyābaddhoti jiyāya baddho. Pathavito muccati, etaṃ ‘‘dvisahassathāma’’nti veditabbaṃ . Lohasīsādīnanti kāḷalohatambalohasīsādīnaṃ. Bhāroti purisabhāro, so pana majjhimapurisassa vasena edisaṃ tassa balaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ. Uggahitasippā dhanuvedasikkhāvasena. Ciṇṇavasībhāvā lakkhesu avirajjhanasarakkhepavasena. Kataṃ rājakulādīsu upagantvā asanaṃ sarakkhepo etehīti katūpasanāti āha ‘‘rājakulādīsu dassitasippā’’ti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      "‘‘Bodhisatto cattāri kaṇḍāni āharī’’ti vatvā tameva atthaṃ vitthārato dassento ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘tadā kirā’’"
      },
      "tiādimāha. Tattha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "javissāmā"
      },
      "ti dhāvissāma. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Aggi uṭṭhahī"
      },
      "ti sīghapatanasantāpena ca sūriyarasmisantāpassa āsannabhāvena ca usumā uṭṭhahi. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Pakkhapañjarenā"
      },
      "ti pakkhajālantarena."
    ],
    "innerText": "‘‘Bodhisatto cattāri kaṇḍāni āharī’’ti vatvā tameva atthaṃ vitthārato dassento ‘‘tadā kirā’’tiādimāha. Tattha javissāmāti dhāvissāma. Aggi uṭṭhahīti sīghapatanasantāpena ca sūriyarasmisantāpassa āsannabhāvena ca usumā uṭṭhahi. Pakkhapañjarenāti pakkhajālantarena."
  },
  {
