    ],
    "innerText": "Nivattitvāti ‘‘nippayojanamidaṃ javana’’nti nivattitvā. Pattakaṭāhena otthaṭapatto viyāti pihitapatto viya ahosi, vegasā patanena nagarassa upari ākāsassa nirikkhaṇaṃ ahosi. Sañcāritattā anekahaṃsasahassasadiso paññāyi seyyathāpi bodhisattassa dhanuggahakāle sarakūṭādidassane."
  },
  {
