        },
        "innerText": "Dukkara"
      },
      "nti tassa adassanaṃ sandhāyāha, na attano patanaṃ. Sūriyamaṇḍalañhi atisīghena javena gacchantampi paññāsayojanāyāmavitthataṃ attano vipulatāya pabhassaratāya ca sattānaṃ cakkhussa gocarabhāvaṃ gacchati, javanahaṃso pana tādisena sūriyena saddhiṃ javena gacchanto na paññāyeyya. Tasmā vuttaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘na sakkā tayā passitu’’"
      },
      "nti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Cattāro"
      },
      " akkhaṇavedhino. Gantvā gahite sotuṃ ghaṇḍaṃ piḷandhāpetvā sayaṃ puratthābhimukho nisinno. Puratthimadisābhimukhaṃ gatakaṇḍaṃ sandhāyāha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘paṭhamakaṇḍeneva saddhiṃ uppatitvā’’"
      },
      "ti. Te cattāri kaṇḍāni ekakkhaṇeyeva khipiṃsu."
    ],
    "innerText": "Dukkaranti tassa adassanaṃ sandhāyāha, na attano patanaṃ. Sūriyamaṇḍalañhi atisīghena javena gacchantampi paññāsayojanāyāmavitthataṃ attano vipulatāya pabhassaratāya ca sattānaṃ cakkhussa gocarabhāvaṃ gacchati, javanahaṃso pana tādisena sūriyena saddhiṃ javena gacchanto na paññāyeyya. Tasmā vuttaṃ ‘‘na sakkā tayā passitu’’nti. Cattāro akkhaṇavedhino. Gantvā gahite sotuṃ ghaṇḍaṃ piḷandhāpetvā sayaṃ puratthābhimukho nisinno. Puratthimadisābhimukhaṃ gatakaṇḍaṃ sandhāyāha ‘‘paṭhamakaṇḍeneva saddhiṃ uppatitvā’’ti. Te cattāri kaṇḍāni ekakkhaṇeyeva khipiṃsu."
  },
  {
