          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "āyusaṅkhāro"
      },
      ". Yathā hi kammajarūpānaṃ pavatti jīvitindriyapaṭibaddhā, evaṃ attabhāvassa pavatti tappaṭibaddhāti. Bahuvacananiddeso pana pāḷiyaṃ ekasmiṃ khaṇe anekasatasaṅkhassa jīvitindriyassa upalabbhanato. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Taṃ"
      },
      " jīvitindriyaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Tato"
      },
      " yathāvuttadevatānaṃ javato ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "sīghataraṃ khīyati"
      },
      " ittarakhaṇattā. Vuttañhetaṃ –"
    ],
    "innerText": "Āyuṃ saṅkharoti etenāti āyusaṅkhāro. Yathā hi kammajarūpānaṃ pavatti jīvitindriyapaṭibaddhā, evaṃ attabhāvassa pavatti tappaṭibaddhāti. Bahuvacananiddeso pana pāḷiyaṃ ekasmiṃ khaṇe anekasatasaṅkhassa jīvitindriyassa upalabbhanato. Taṃ jīvitindriyaṃ. Tato yathāvuttadevatānaṃ javato sīghataraṃ khīyati ittarakhaṇattā. Vuttañhetaṃ –"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Jīvitaṃ attabhāvo ca, sukhadukkhā ca kevalā;"
