    },
    "innerText": "7. Āṇisuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "229"
      },
      ". Aññe rājāno ca bhāgaṃ gaṇhantā ime viya dasabhāgaṃ gaṇhantīti tesamayaṃ anugati paññāyati. Mahājanassa ānayanato ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "ānako"
      },
      "ti āha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘evaṃladdhanāmo’’"
      },
      "ti. Idāni taṃ ādito paṭṭhāya āgamanānukkamaṃ dassetuṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘himavante kirā’’"
      },
      "tiādimāha. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Kareṇu"
      },
      "nti kareṇukaṃ, hatthininti attho. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Sakkariṃsū"
      },
      "ti anatthapariharaṇavasena pasatthūpahāravasena ca pūjesuṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Otarī"
      },
      "ti kuḷīradahaṃ pāvisi. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Paṭikkamitvā"
      },
      " ṭhapanavasena apakkamitvā ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "pati"
      },
      "."
    ],
    "innerText": "229. Aññe rājāno ca bhāgaṃ gaṇhantā ime viya dasabhāgaṃ gaṇhantīti tesamayaṃ anugati paññāyati. Mahājanassa ānayanato ānakoti āha ‘‘evaṃladdhanāmo’’ti. Idāni taṃ ādito paṭṭhāya āgamanānukkamaṃ dassetuṃ ‘‘himavante kirā’’tiādimāha. Kareṇunti kareṇukaṃ, hatthininti attho. Sakkariṃsūti anatthapariharaṇavasena pasatthūpahāravasena ca pūjesuṃ. Otarīti kuḷīradahaṃ pāvisi. Paṭikkamitvā ṭhapanavasena apakkamitvā pati."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Suvaṇṇarajatādimaya"
      },
      "nti kismiñci chidde suvaṇṇamayaṃ, kismiñci rajatamayaṃ, kismiñci phalikamayaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "āṇiṃ ghaṭayiṃsu"
      },
      " bandhiṃsu. Pubbe pharitvā tiṭṭhantassa dvādasa yojanāni pamāṇo etassāti ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "dvādasayojanappamāṇo,"
      },
      " saddo. Athassa anekasatakāle gacchante ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "antosālāyampi dukkhena suyyittha"
      },
      " āṇisaṅghāṭamattattā."
    ],
    "innerText": "Suvaṇṇarajatādimayanti kismiñci chidde suvaṇṇamayaṃ, kismiñci rajatamayaṃ, kismiñci phalikamayaṃ āṇiṃ ghaṭayiṃsu bandhiṃsu. Pubbe pharitvā tiṭṭhantassa dvādasa yojanāni pamāṇo etassāti dvādasayojanappamāṇo, saddo. Athassa anekasatakāle gacchante antosālāyampi dukkhena suyyittha āṇisaṅghāṭamattattā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Gambhīrā"
      },
      "ti agādhā dukkhogāḷhā. Sallasuttañhi ‘‘animittamanaññāta’’ntiādinā pāḷivasena gambhīraṃ, na atthagambhīraṃ. Tathā hi tattha tā tā gāthā duviññeyyarūpā tiṭṭhanti, duviññeyyaṃ ñāṇena dukkhogāhanti katvā ‘‘gambhīra’’nti ",
      " vuccati. Pubbāparampettha kāsañci gāthānaṃ duviññeyyatāya dukkhogāhameva, tasmā taṃ pāḷivasena ‘‘gambhīra’’nti vuttaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘pāḷivasena gambhīrā sallasuttasadisā’’"
      },
      "ti. Iminā nayena ‘‘atthavasena gambhīrā’’ti ettha attho veditabbo. Mahāvedallasuttassa atthavasena gambhīratā pākaṭāyeva. Lokaṃ uttaratīti lokuttaro, navavidhaappamāṇadhammo, so atthabhūto etesaṃ atthīti ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "lokuttarā"
      },
      ". Tenāha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘lokuttaraatthadīpakā’’"
      },
      "ti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Sattasuññatadhammamattamevā"
      },
      "ti sattena attanā suññataṃ kevalaṃ dhammamattameva. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Uggahetabbaṃ pariyāpuṇitabba"
      },
      "nti ca liṅgavacanavipallāsena vuttanti āha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘uggahetabbe ca pariyāpuṇitabbe cā’’"
      },
      "ti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Kavitā"
      },
      "ti kavino kammaṃ kavikatā. Yassa pana yaṃ kammaṃ, taṃ tena katanti vuccatīti āha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘kavitāti kavīhi katā’’"
      },
      "ti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Itaraṃ"
      },
      " ‘‘kāveyyā’’ti padaṃ, kabbanti vuttaṃ hoti. ‘‘Kabba’’nti ca kavinā vuttanti attho. Tenāha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘tasseva vevacana’’"
      },
      "nti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Cittakkharā"
      },
      "ti vicitrākāraakkharā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Sāsanato bahibhūtā"
      },
      "ti na sāsanāvacarā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Tesaṃ sāvakehī"
      },
      "ti ‘‘buddhānaṃ sāvakā’’ti ",
      " apaññātānaṃ yesaṃ kesañci sāvakehi. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Anuggayhamānā"
      },
      "ti na uggayhamānā savanadhāraṇaparicayaatthūpaparikkhādivasena anuggayhamānā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Antaradhāyanti"
      },
      " adassanaṃ gacchanti."
    ],
    "innerText": "Gambhīrāti agādhā dukkhogāḷhā. Sallasuttañhi ‘‘animittamanaññāta’’ntiādinā pāḷivasena gambhīraṃ, na atthagambhīraṃ. Tathā hi tattha tā tā gāthā duviññeyyarūpā tiṭṭhanti, duviññeyyaṃ ñāṇena dukkhogāhanti katvā ‘‘gambhīra’’nti vuccati. Pubbāparampettha kāsañci gāthānaṃ duviññeyyatāya dukkhogāhameva, tasmā taṃ pāḷivasena ‘‘gambhīra’’nti vuttaṃ ‘‘pāḷivasena gambhīrā sallasuttasadisā’’ti. Iminā nayena ‘‘atthavasena gambhīrā’’ti ettha attho veditabbo. Mahāvedallasuttassa atthavasena gambhīratā pākaṭāyeva. Lokaṃ uttaratīti lokuttaro, navavidhaappamāṇadhammo, so atthabhūto etesaṃ atthīti lokuttarā. Tenāha ‘‘lokuttaraatthadīpakā’’ti. Sattasuññatadhammamattamevāti sattena attanā suññataṃ kevalaṃ dhammamattameva. Uggahetabbaṃ pariyāpuṇitabbanti ca liṅgavacanavipallāsena vuttanti āha ‘‘uggahetabbe ca pariyāpuṇitabbe cā’’ti. Kavitāti kavino kammaṃ kavikatā. Yassa pana yaṃ kammaṃ, taṃ tena katanti vuccatīti āha ‘‘kavitāti kavīhi katā’’ti. Itaraṃ ‘‘kāveyyā’’ti padaṃ, kabbanti vuttaṃ hoti. ‘‘Kabba’’nti ca kavinā vuttanti attho. Tenāha ‘‘tasseva vevacana’’nti. Cittakkharāti vicitrākāraakkharā. Sāsanato bahibhūtāti na sāsanāvacarā. Tesaṃ sāvakehīti ‘‘buddhānaṃ sāvakā’’ti apaññātānaṃ yesaṃ kesañci sāvakehi. Anuggayhamānāti na uggayhamānā savanadhāraṇaparicayaatthūpaparikkhādivasena anuggayhamānā. Antaradhāyanti adassanaṃ gacchanti."
  },
  {
