    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "9. Nāgasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "231"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Atikkantavela"
      },
      "nti bhattānumodanaupanisinnakathāvelato atikkantavelaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Asambhinnenā"
      },
      "ti sarasampattito asambhinnena, sarassa uccāraṇasampattiṃ aparihāpetvāti attho. Aparisuddhāsayatāya ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "neva guṇavaṇṇāya na ñāṇabalāya hoti. Ta"
      },
      "nti taṃ tathā paccayānaṃ paribhuñjanaṃ, taṃ tathā micchāpaṭipajjanaṃ."
    ],
    "innerText": "231.Atikkantavelanti bhattānumodanaupanisinnakathāvelato atikkantavelaṃ. Asambhinnenāti sarasampattito asambhinnena, sarassa uccāraṇasampattiṃ aparihāpetvāti attho. Aparisuddhāsayatāya neva guṇavaṇṇāya na ñāṇabalāya hoti. Tanti taṃ tathā paccayānaṃ paribhuñjanaṃ, taṃ tathā micchāpaṭipajjanaṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Nāgasuttavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "10. Biḷārasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "232"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Gharānaṃ"
      },
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "sandhī"
      },
      "ti gharena gharassa sambandhaṭṭhānaṃ. Saha malena vattatīti ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "samalaṃ"
      },
      ". Gehato gāmato ca nikkhamanacandanikaṭṭhānaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Saṅkāraṭṭhāna"
      },
      "nti saṅkārakūṭaṃ. Keci ‘‘sandhisaṅkārakūṭaṭṭhāna’’nti vadanti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Vuṭṭhāna"
      },
      "nti āpannaāpattito, na kilesato vuṭṭhānaṃ, suddhante adhiṭṭhānaṃ. Taṃ pana yathāāpannāya āpattiyā ‘‘desanā’’tveva vuccatīti āha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘desanā paññāyatī’’"
      },
      "ti."
    ],
    "innerText": "232.Gharānaṃsandhīti gharena gharassa sambandhaṭṭhānaṃ. Saha malena vattatīti samalaṃ. Gehato gāmato ca nikkhamanacandanikaṭṭhānaṃ. Saṅkāraṭṭhānanti saṅkārakūṭaṃ. Keci ‘‘sandhisaṅkārakūṭaṭṭhāna’’nti vadanti. Vuṭṭhānanti āpannaāpattito, na kilesato vuṭṭhānaṃ, suddhante adhiṭṭhānaṃ. Taṃ pana yathāāpannāya āpattiyā ‘‘desanā’’tveva vuccatīti āha ‘‘desanā paññāyatī’’ti."
  },
