    ],
    "innerText": "233.Ettakampīti iminā jarasiṅgālena laddhabbaṃ cittassādamattampi na labhissati sakalameva kappaṃ sabbaso avīcijālāhi nirantaraṃ jhāyamānatāya niccadukkhāturabhāvato."
